News

* LinkSmart 2.2.1 available

  Finally, LinkSmart 2.2.1 is now available. This major 
  enhancements of this release are:
  
  * Apache Karaf based OSGi execution environment
  * different deployment modes (full, light etc) are available
  * New tunnel service
  * New backbones for binary messages and for local OSGi services
  * New component for handling large messages
  * New handshake protocol between NetworkManagers
  * Improved test coverage
  * Internal handling of message encoding improved
  * Many, many bug fixes